Subject:Attracting Love
I do not know what to start with that’s why I'll start by telling you about myself. 
I consider myself quite a knowledgeable and clever lady, also I am  very pretty and romantic. 
I adore kids, and I feel that it is time to have my own children.. It seems to be foolish to describe imaginary image of a loved one. 
I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my soul mate. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is not everything. The inner beauty is much more important than beauty of the body. I want my man to be ambitious, communicative and with good sense of humor. 
And I want to love my man with all my heart and soul http://cogevula.digital-cn.ru Let's start our acquaintance

